data.name: ReadAdministrativeAction1
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.TYPE from CKT_ADMIN_ACTION T1 join CKT_ADMIN_ACT_CERT T2 on (T1.TYPE = @type) and (T1.TYPE = T2.AAT_TYPE)
